Top 200 Most Memorable Soundtracks

by vincent-roy-officiel • Created 11 years ago • Modified 11 years ago
In this list I ranked the 200 most unforgettable movie (and some TV show) soundtracks based on their knowledge by the large public, their popularity, the general greatness of the score or the songs and their impact on cinema or the Television. Please leave comments and corrections. Enjoy !
